Name: Solo (James Bourne)
Description: James Bourne was drafted to a top-secret special forces operation where he endured ten months of hard and brutal training to earn his place in the new counter-terrorist group Omega Strike.
FirstComicDescription: Guest-starring Captain America! As tensions boil over in Symkaria, Cap provides an assist to Spider-Man and Silver Sable. Will the trio be able to pull off a heist of ULTIMATUM's HQ? More truths revealed about the mysterious Solo.
